Property Brothers at Home - Season 3, Episode 4 (Drew's Honeymoon House)




Make Room for Guests

Jonathan has lived with Drew his entire life but now he's helping his brother move into the Los Angeles fixer-upper he bought with his fiancee Linda. At the top of their renovation wish list is a guest suite that will serve as a home away from home for Jonathan. With just 12 weeks to totally transform the house before a pre-wedding party, the brothers tackle a self-contained guest suite as well as two luxurious guest bedrooms.




Original Air Date: 13-Dec-2017
